#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_product_template__cost_method
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_stock_quant__cost_method
msgid ""
"Standard Price: The products are valued at their standard cost defined on the product.\n"
"        Average Cost (AVCO): The products are valued at weighted average cost.\n"
"        First In First Out (FIFO): The products are valued supposing those that enter the company first will also leave it first.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"ລາຄາມາດຕະຖານ: ສິນຄ້າຈະຖືກຕີມູນຄ່າຕາມຕົ້ນທຶນມາດຕະຖານທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ໃນສິນຄ້າ.\n"
"        ຕົ້ນທຶນສະເລ່ຍ (AVCO): ສິນຄ້າຈະຖືກຕີມູນຄ່າຕາມຕົ້ນທຶນສະເລ່ຍຖ່ວງນ້ຳໜັກ.\n"
"        ເຂົ້າກ່ອນ ອອກກ່ອນ (FIFO): ສິນຄ້າຈະຖືກຕີມູນຄ່າໂດຍສົມມຸດວ່າສິນຄ້າທີ່ເຂົ້າບໍລິສັດກ່ອນຈະອອກໄປກ່ອ"
"ນ.\n"
"        "

