#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_stock_location__valuation_in_account_id
msgid ""
"Used for real-time inventory valuation. When set on a virtual location (non "
"internal type), this account will be used to hold the value of products "
"being moved from an internal location into this location, instead of the "
"generic Stock Output Account set on the product. This has no effect for "
"internal locations."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ສຳລັບການຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າແບບ Real-time. ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນສະຖານທີ່ສະເມືອນ (virtual location), ບັນ"
"ຊີນີ້ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອເກັບມູນຄ່າຂອງສິນຄ້າທີ່ຖືກຍ້າຍຈາກສະຖານທີ່ພາຍໃນເຂົ້າມາໃນສະຖານທີ່ນີ້, ແທນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ບັນຊີສະຕັອກ"
"ຂາອອກທົ່ວໄປທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນສິນຄ້າ. ນີ້ບໍ່ມີຜົນກັບສະຖານທີ່ພາຍໃນ."

#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_stock_location__valuation_out_account_id
msgid ""
"Used for real-time inventory valuation. When set on a virtual location (non "
"internal type), this account will be used to hold the value of products "
"being moved out of this location and into an internal location, instead of "
"the generic Stock Output Account set on the product. This has no effect for "
"internal locations."
msgstr ""
"ໃຊ້ສຳລັບການຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າແບບ Real-time. ເມື່ອຕັ້ງຄ່າໃນສະຖານທີ່ສະເມືອນ (virtual location), ບັນ"
"ຊີນີ້ຈະຖືກໃຊ້ເພື່ອເກັບມູນຄ່າຂອງສິນຄ້າທີ່ຖືກຍ້າຍອອກຈາກສະຖານທີ່ນີ້ເຂົ້າໄປໃນສະຖານທີ່ພາຍໃນ, ແທນທີ່ຈະໃຊ້ບັນຊີສະ"
"ຕັອກຂາອອກທົ່ວໄປທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນສິນຄ້າ. ນີ້ບໍ່ມີຜົນກັບສະຖານທີ່ພາຍໃນ."

