#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_product_category__property_stock_valuation_account_id
msgid ""
"When automated inventory valuation is enabled on a product, this account "
"will hold the current value of the products."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອເປີດການຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ບັນຊີນີ້ຈະເກັບມູນຄ່າປັດຈຸບັນຂອງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_product_category__property_stock_account_output_categ_id
msgid ""
"When doing automated inventory valuation, counterpart journal items for all outgoing stock moves will be posted in this account,\n"
"                unless there is a specific valuation account set on the destination location. This is the default value for all products in this category.\n"
"                It can also directly be set on each product."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຕີມູນຄ່າແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ລາຍການບັນຊີຄູ່ສຳລັບການເຄື່ອນໄຫວສະຕັອກຂາອອກທັງໝົດຈະຖືກລົງໃນບັນຊີນີ້,\n"
"                ເວັ້ນເສຍແຕ່ຈະມີບັນຊີການຕີມູນຄ່າສະເພາະທີ່ຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນສະຖານທີ່ປາຍທາງ. ນີ້ແມ່ນຄ່າມາດຕະຖ"
"ານສຳລັບສິນຄ້າທັງໝົດໃນໝວດນີ້.\n"
"                ມັນຍັງສາມາດຕັ້ງໂດຍກົງໃສ່ແຕ່ລະສິນຄ້າໄດ້."

#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:stock_account.field_product_category__property_stock_journal
msgid ""
"When doing automated inventory valuation, this is the Accounting Journal in "
"which entries will be automatically posted when stock moves are processed."
msgstr ""
"ໃນການຕີມູນຄ່າແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ນີ້ແມ່ນປຶ້ມບັນຊີທີ່ຈະລົງລາຍການໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດເມື່ອການເຄື່ອນໄຫວສະຕັອກຖືກປະມ"
"ວນຜົນ."

#. module: stock_account
#: model:ir.model,name:stock_account.model_stock_valuation_layer_revaluation
msgid "Wizard model to reavaluate a stock inventory for a product"
msgstr "ແບບຟອມຊ່ວຍ (Wizard) ເພື່ອຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າຄົງຄັງໃໝ່ສຳລັບສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_lot.py:0
#: code:addons/stock_account/wizard/stock_valuation_layer_revaluation.py:0
msgid "You cannot adjust the valuation of a layer with zero quantity"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປັບການຕີມູນຄ່າຂອງຊັ້ນທີ່ມີຈຳນວນເປັນສູນໄດ້"

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/wizard/stock_valuation_layer_revaluation.py:0
msgid "You cannot adjust valuation without a product"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປັບການຕີມູນຄ່າໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ມີສິນຄ້າ"

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot change the costing method of product valuated by lot/serial "
"number."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນວິທີການຕົ້ນທຶນຂອງສິນຄ້າທີ່ຕີມູນຄ່າຕາມ ເລກລັອດ/ເລກຊີຣີ ໄດ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot change the product category of a product valuated by lot/serial "
"number."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດປ່ຽນໝວດສິນຄ້າຂອງສິນຄ້າທີ່ຕີມູນຄ່າຕາມ ເລກລັອດ/ເລກຊີຣີ ໄດ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/wizard/stock_valuation_layer_revaluation.py:0
msgid "You cannot revalue a product with a standard cost method."
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າທີ່ໃຊ້ວິທີການຕົ້ນທຶນມາດຕະຖານໃໝ່ໄດ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/wizard/stock_valuation_layer_revaluation.py:0
msgid "You cannot revalue a product with an empty or negative stock."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າໃໝ່ໄດ້ ຫາກສິນຄ້າໃນສະຕັອກຫວ່າງເປົ່າ ຫຼື ຕິດລົບ."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/wizard/stock_valuation_layer_revaluation.py:0
msgid "You cannot revalue multiple products at once"
msgstr "ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດຕີມູນຄ່າສິນຄ້າຫຼາຍລາຍການໃໝ່ພ້ອມກັນໄດ້"

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_lot.py:0
msgid ""
"You cannot update the cost of a product in automated valuation as it leads "
"to the creation of a journal entry, for which you don't have the access "
"rights."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດອັບເດດຕົ້ນທຶນສິນຄ້າໃນການຕີມູນຄ່າແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດໄດ້ ເນື່ອງຈາກມັນຈະສ້າງລາຍການບັນຊີ ເຊິ່ງທ່ານບໍ່"
"ມີສິດເຂົ້າເຖິງ."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
msgid ""
"You don't have any input valuation account defined on your product category."
" You must define one before processing this operation."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ກຳນົດບັນຊີຕີມູນຄ່າຂາເຂົ້າໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດມັນກ່ອນດຳເນີນການນີ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
msgid ""
"You don't have any output valuation account defined on your product "
"category. You must define one before processing this operation."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ກຳນົດບັນຊີຕີມູນຄ່າຂາອອກໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດມັນກ່ອນດຳເນີນການນີ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
msgid ""
"You don't have any stock input account defined on your product category. You"
" must define one before processing this operation."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ກຳນົດບັນຊີສະຕັອກຂາເຂົ້າໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດມັນກ່ອນດຳເນີນການນີ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_move.py:0
msgid ""
"You don't have any stock journal defined on your product category, check if "
"you have installed a chart of accounts."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ກຳນົດປຶ້ມບັນຊີສະຕັອກໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າ, ກະລຸນາກວດເບິ່ງວ່າທ່ານໄດ້ຕິດຕັ້ງຜັງບັນຊີແລ້ວບໍ່."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/product.py:0
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_move.py:0
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_valuation_layer.py:0
msgid ""
"You don't have any stock valuation account defined on your product category."
" You must define one before processing this operation."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ທັນໄດ້ກຳນົດບັນຊີຕີມູນຄ່າສະຕັອກໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າ. ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດມັນກ່ອນດຳເນີນການນີ້."

#. module: stock_account
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/stock_account/models/stock_valuation_layer.py:0
msgid "You must set a counterpart account on your product category."
msgstr "ທ່ານຕ້ອງກຳນົດບັນຊີຄູ່ສັນຍາໃນໝວດສິນຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: stock_account
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:stock_account.stock_valuation_layer_revaluation_form_view
